NAME
    taskell - Command-line Kanban board for task management

SYNOPSIS
    taskell [options] [file]

DESCRIPTION
    taskell is a command-line task management application that creates an interactive Kanban board in your terminal. It allows you to organize tasks into lists, move them between lists, and manage your workflow efficiently.

OPTIONS
    -h, --help              Show help message
    -v, --version           Show version information
    -n, --new               Create a new board
    -t, --template <file>   Use a template file
    -d, --dump              Dump board as JSON
    -i, --import <file>     Import tasks from a JSON file
    -e, --export <file>     Export tasks to a JSON file
    --config <file>         Use a custom config file
    --theme <theme>         Use a specific color theme

USAGE
    taskell [options] [file]

EXAMPLES
    taskell
    taskell myboard.md
    taskell -n newboard.md
    taskell -t template.md myboard.md
    taskell -d > board_backup.json
    taskell -i imported_tasks.json myboard.md

OUTPUT
    taskell displays an interactive Kanban board in the terminal, showing tasks organized into lists.
